OL,4,Cholidays: an anachronism
OL,6,GRemember the good old days of the
OL,7,GBritish bank holiday? A day off work
OL,8,Gfor millions. Maybe a trip to the
OL,9,Gseaside?
OL,11,FThese days bank holidays are very
OL,12,Fdifferent.
OL,14,FWhile some companies still give their
OL,15,Fstaff the day off, many businesses
OL,16,Fopen as usual. On a typical high
OL,17,Fstreet everything will be open apart
OL,18,Ffrom the banks.
