OL,4,Cholidays: an anachronism
OL,6,FFor many of us who will be working
OL,7,Fnormally, the only real evidence of a
OL,8,Fbank holiday is the TV schedule.
OL,10,FThe major channels still depart from
OL,11,Ftheir normal schedules on Bank Holiday
OL,12,FMondays, though to nothing like the
OL,13,Fextent they used to.
OL,15,FNot so long ago, it was very different.
