OL,3,CShorter news programmes on bank
OL,4,Cholidays: an anachronism
OL,6,FYes, there may need to be a bit more
OL,7,Fforeign news or pre-planned items.
OL,8,FThere would be nothing from the courts
OL,9,For parliament. But there are plenty of
OL,10,Fgood stories ` especially issue-driven
OL,11,Fpieces and human stories ` which can
OL,12,Fbe squeezed out on busy days.
OL,14,FI cannot believe Wales, Scotland and
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland would face problems
OL,16,Fproviding a normal half-hour programme
OL,17,Fat 6.30pm either.
